119
00:06:17,822 --> 00:06:18,860
It's tonight.

120
00:06:18,860 --> 00:06:19,838
Tonight?

121
00:06:19,838 --> 00:06:21,436
OK I'll leave my schedule open.

122
00:06:21,436 --> 00:06:22,894
Really?

123
00:06:23,472 --> 00:06:25,359
Thank you so much!

124
00:06:25,359 --> 00:06:27,435
Don't cry.

125
00:06:27,435 --> 00:06:29,108
A matching party?

126
00:06:29,441 --> 00:06:30,849
