159
00:07:45,584 --> 00:07:49,329
The act with the glasses was so pathetic he had me shivering.

160
00:07:49,329 --> 00:07:52,145
I'll tear them apart with my bare hands!!

161
00:07:52,145 --> 00:07:53,516
Wait, senpai!

162
00:07:54,929 --> 00:07:57,810
I wonder if everything went ok.

163
00:07:58,041 --> 00:07:59,314
Hm?

164
00:07:59,314 --> 00:08:00,881
Uh.. well...

165
00:08:00,881 --> 00:08:05,929
It's just that it seemed your friends
looked angry when we left the store.

166
00:08:06,814 --> 00:08:10,376
I think they had a good time.

167
00:08:10,376 --> 00:08:13,551
I had a good time too.

168
00:08:13,551 --> 00:08:17,600
I'm glad you said that.

169
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,975
