173
00:08:34,586 --> 00:08:36,339
No.

174
00:08:37,097 --> 00:08:39,378
You can sleep if you want.

175
00:08:39,537 --> 00:08:41,841
I'll wake you before you get to your station.

176
00:08:41,841 --> 00:08:44,444
I'm all right.

177
00:08:44,721 --> 00:08:46,900
Well ok.

178
