181
00:09:10,275 --> 00:09:11,089
Um.

182
00:09:11,788 --> 00:09:13,122
Yes?

183
00:09:17,842 --> 00:09:21,424
I can accompany you home if you'd like.

184
00:09:22,658 --> 00:09:24,643
That's ok.

185
00:09:24,643 --> 00:09:25,842
Thank you for the thought.

186
00:09:26,244 --> 00:09:27,851
