238
00:12:45,795 --> 00:12:48,993
[It turns out I wasn't just imagining it]

239
00:12:49,427 --> 00:12:54,498
[I found all these pictures of myself in my mailbox just now]

240
00:12:59,476 --> 00:13:00,250
