241
00:13:03,657 --> 00:13:05,780
An emergency just came up.

242
00:13:05,780 --> 00:13:08,403
It looks like someone's following Hermes-san around.

243
00:13:08,403 --> 00:13:11,076
[Stalker]

244
00:13:11,076 --> 00:13:13,491
What!!

245
00:13:13,491 --> 00:13:16,293
